title: MFSL MFCD 850 - 921 SILVER PACK #3 ALAC
description:
Here is the THIRD AND FINAL of the MFCD collection Or MF cd collection as I like to call it. This is going to be near impossible to complete due to its obscurity. I have an extensive range of sources but found none of the gospel ones or many of the Russian classical releases. However what is here is quite good. Hopefully more will be uploaded by others. Enjoy!
